= ICU Ward Round Checklist =

[] Start enteral feed if appropriate
[] Bowel review
[] Ventilator bundle
[] How old are the lines
[] Lines removed if not needed
[] Antibiotic review
[] IV drugs be converted to enteral where possible
[] Drugs discontinued where possible
[] Physiotherapy input
[] Communication with relatives/patient
[] Discharge summary updated